%N A015989 Inverse of 1980th cyclotomic polynomial.
%C A015989 Periodic with period length 1980. - _Ray Chandler_, Apr 07 2017
%H A015989 Ray Chandler, <a href="/A015989/b015989.txt">Table of n, a(n) for n = 0..2000</a>
%H A015989 <a href="/index/Per#periodic">Index entries for periodic sequences</a>, period 1980.
%H A015989 <a href="/index/Rec#order_480">Index entries for linear recurrences with constant coefficients</a>, order 480.
